data.description: Located in the heart the Village of Swartz Creek with walking distance to the schools, restaurants and other amenities downtown this 3 bedroom cape cod is ready for new owners. First floor primary bedroom. Lots of natural hardwood flooring. Large fenced yard and a detached 2 car garage to hold all your toys! Furnace is 8 years old and New Windows installed 2018.
